                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030112-92-defend673 t18030112-92-punish497"></join>
               Privately whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before the Lord Chief Baron.</p>
